#summary List of bot system commands with brief overview and permission level

 = System commands =
 
 Commands listed below are treated as *system commands*. They performs system or admin actions and require high access level. See [CommandSyntax Command syntax]
 * *Register user*

 Registers new user with given JID and access level
 
 Syntax: _admin reg user {usr_jid} {access_level}


 * *Grant access*

 Changes access level for given user
